      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YOU NEVER LOSE (6) goes very well this trip starting 16 times for nine wins and four minors. Was out of placings last time (30.39) at Wentworth Park in a Mix 1/2/3, finishing fifth and beaten 10 lengths. Looks the one to beat with even luck. IMPATIENT ROSE (1) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (23.14) at this track over 400m. Expecting another good run. FLYING MONKEY'S (5) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.13. Awkwardly drawn but has a good record over this journey. Leading chance again. THAT'S MINE (2) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
